Could tell someone had died just hearing my friend call me to say good morning in neutral tone. His grandpa passed away. Walking around talking, ten minutes later we get a phone call, someone stabbed bleeding in my other homie's bathroom, drove him to hospital. Morning of sorrow.

With every year my city resembled that Dishonored video game more. Half-drunk half-mad homeless people accosting you on the street for money or ranting about delusions. Abandoned industrial buildings housing drug addicts. Acutely feeling an absence when not carrying any weapons.

Doing chin-ups in the park, some 70 year old ex-Navy homeless looking guy with bloodshot eyes comes to tell me how he used to do pull-ups w/ an 80 kg/175 lbs. barbell when he weighed less himself, was strongest of 5000 soldiers. Multiple heart attacks already, not much time left.

Told me how they would do their grueling military training and then do bodybuilding exercises on their own afterwards, using DIY weights and barbells they made using shipbuilding facility equipment. No one else had such physique in town. Didn't ask for money, just wanted to talk.

Every poor neighborhood starts spawning criminal types that roam around all day acting familiar following normal people around and asking for drug money and cigarettes and if you try to refuse them they start threatening and acting aggressive so people are forced to indulge them.

It's like a vicious cycle of abuse where they act like someone's friend and ask for alcohol or to loan money and if he tells them to go away they start threatening his family and stuff so he just gives them cash and then they immediately go back to acting like his friend, horror.

Really should just never let your friends get involved with such people because there's basically no going back and it's an endless cycle of daily stress and them dragging you down too and forcing you to do criminal stuff until you're one of them addicted to drugs and ruined too.

47 year old pedophile drug dealer dating a 13 year old hooked to heroin and meth with her parents non-functional barely sentient drug addicts too gets stolen from him by a 25 year old career criminal when she turns 17, dealer drinks himself to death now. A small taste of my town.
